special_powers.name: JUST A FRIENDLY HANDSHAKE

special_powers.name: BLOCKING REPULSOR BLASTS

special_powers.name: LEADING THE RESISTANCE

special_powers.name: I WANTED TO TALK, BUT...

special_powers.name: PHOTONIC ABSORBTION
special_powers.description: When Ms. Marvel is hit by a character that can use Penetrating/Psychic Blast or Pulse Wave, after actions resolve remove an action token from her. If you can't, heal her 1 click. This can't be ignored.

special_powers.name: "FAIR" GRECO-ROMAN WRESTLING

special_powers.name: HIDDEN AGENDA

special_powers.name: HELPING WITH ALL 42 PLANS

special_powers.name: UNBREAKABLE SKIN

When Bullseye targets a character with a Marked token with an attack, he may remove one Marked token from that character to increase the damage dealt to that character by 1 if he hits.

special_powers.name: I TOOK OUT THE AVENGERS ONCE. MOST OF THEM.

special_powers.name: TURNS OUT THE NAME'S TONY, NOT RALPH

If you do, at the beginning of your first turn give that character an action token.

special_powers.name: INFILTRATION SUIT DAMPENERS

special_powers.name: HE'S ON OUR SIDE AND DOES WHAT I SAY

special_powers.name: UNSTABLE
special_powers.description: STOP. Sentry can use Impervious. When this click is revealed, roll a d6 that can't be rerolled. Until you roll for this power again, even if this power is lost, modify Sentry's combat values by the results. This can't be countered or ignored. 1: -1; 2 - 4: 0; 5 - 6: +1

special_powers.name: EVERYONE'S LOOKING OUT FOR ME AND MY FAMILY...OR OUT LOOKING FOR THEM

special_powers.name: THOR JUST KILLED GOLIATH...

special_powers.name: KING OF ATLANTIS

special_powers.name: IMPERIUS REX!

special_powers.name: WARRIOR OF ATLANTIS
special_powers.description: Atlantean Warrior has the Atlantis keyword. Atlantean Warrior's move actions don't count against your action total.

special_powers.name: RETREAT FROM MY FRIEND'S MADNESS

special_powers.name: CONCENTRATION BROKEN
special_powers.description: At the end of your turn, place a Concentration token on this card. When Dr. Strange would take damage from an opponent's attack, instead turn Dr. Strange to the click number (minimum click #1) equal to 7 minus the number of Concentration tokens, then remove all Concentration tokens.

special_powers.name: TRY NOT TO HURT EACH OTHER

special_powers.name: TONY'S LEGACY

special_powers.name: COMBAT BOOTS AND BOOT JETS

special_powers.name: TECHNOLOGY AND TRAINING
